               <msContents>
                  <summary>Epistles of Paul, መልእክታተ፡ ጳውሎስ፡; Pp. 1-17: Introductions for Paul's Epistles; Pp. 19-41: Romans; Pp. 41-63: 1 Corinthians; Pp. 63-78: 2 Corinthians; Pp. 78-85: Galatians; Pp. 85-92: Ephesians; Pp. 92-97: Philippians; Pp. 97-102: Colossians; Pp. 102-103: 1 Thessalonian, incomplete at tghe end. Images of Pp. 104-151 are missing from the manuscript.  Pp. 152-156: 2 Peter; Pp. 156-162: 1 John; Pp. 162-163: 2 John; Pp. 163: 3 John; Pp. 163-169: James; Pp. 169-171: Jude; Pp. 173-231: Acts of the Apostles, ግብረ፡ ሐዋርያት።; Pp. 232-234:  Introduction to Revelation; Pp. 235-262: Revelation, ራዕየ፡ ዮሐንስ። Pp. 263-292: መዝገበ፡ ሃይማኖት , Theological Treatise, Mazagaba Haymanot.  Pp. 292-306: Book of Light, Matsehafa Berhan.  Pp 306-309: ጊዮርጊስ ወልደ አሚድ, History of the World by Giyorgis Son of Amid.  P. 311: Crude drawings of Dog, Goat, and Lion.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2r" to="10r">Fols 2r–10r</locus>
                     <title>Introduction to the Pauline Epistles</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     
                     <title>New Testament. Selections</title>
                     <note>Romans; 1 Corinthians; 2 Corinthians; Galatians; Ephesians; Philippians; Colossians; 1 Thessalonians; [2 Thessalonians; 1 Timothy; 2 Timothy; Titus; Philemon; Hebrews]; 1 Peter; 2 Peter; 1 John; 2 John; 3 John; James; Jude; Acts; Revelation</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     
                     <title>Preface to the Apocalypse of John</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     
                     <title>Mazgaba Hāymānot</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     
                     <title>Fekkārē Hāymānot</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     
                     <title>Creed by Jacob Baradaeus (CPG, no. 7197)</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     
                     <title>ጊዮርጊስ ወልደ አሚድ</title>
                     
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
